Nuclear and Toxic Missle Prefarb

This is one old project of mine which i though i could share with you.
There is 2 kinds of "missles" which when activated explode with pretty neat different effects (glow,smoke,explosion).
You can use it for anything you want (inspiration, map etc.) i just had fun with it.
All non-crucial parts are grouped up in editor.Missle "war heads" are the main triggers.If you have any questions email me at grave.productions@gmail.com
Have fun.
.vmf and .bsp file included.

teh_grave.
